        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Zoom is the default expectation for external business meetings in Japan — sending a Zoom link to a Japanese client is universally understood. For internal meetings, it depends on the organization: large enterprises use Teams, Google Workspace shops use Meet, and smaller organizations often use Zoom internally as well. If in doubt for external meetings, use Zoom."
      }
